{"title_page": "List of chuches in the Roman Catholic Diocese of Sacramento", "text_new": "This is a list of current and former [[Roman Catholicism in the United States|Roman Catholic]] churches in the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Sacramento]]. The diocese consists of 12 deaneries covering 20 counties in northwest [[California]] and includes the cities of [[Sacramento, California|Sacramento]], [[Vallejo, California|Vallejo]], [[Redding, California|Redding]], [[Fairfield, California|Fairfield]], and [[Chico, California|Chico]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Diocese of Sacramento 2019 Directory|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|year=2019|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/sites/default/files/2019-10/SCD-Directory-Rev11.pdf}}</ref> \n\nThe mother church of the Diocese is the [[Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament in Sacramento|Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament]] in Sacramento. The Diocese also includes several parishes dating from the time of the [[California Gold Rush]] in the 1850s: St. Canice in [[Nevada City, California|Nevada City]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Canice Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-canice-parish-nevada-city}}</ref> Immaculate Conception in [[Downieville, California|Downieville]];<ref>{{cite web|title=Immaculate Conception Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/immaculate-conception-parish-downieville}}</ref> St. Patrick in [[Weaverville, California|Weaverville]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Patrick Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-patrick-parish-weaverville}}</ref> St. Dominic in [[Benicia, California|Benicia]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Dominic Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-dominic-parish-benicia}}</ref> and St. Joseph in [[Marysville, California|Marysville]].<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Joseph Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-joseph-parish-marysville}}</ref> \n\n==City Deanery==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:75%\"\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"30%\" |'''Name'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10%\" |'''Image'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"30%\" |'''Location'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"15\" |'''Established'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10\" |'''Sources'''\n|-\n|[[Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament (Sacramento, California)|Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament]]\n|[[File:CathBSlow.jpg|100px]]\n|1017 11th St, [[Sacramento, California|Sacramento]]\n|1889\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/cathedral-blessed-sacrament-sacramento}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cathedral History|publisher=Cathedral of Blessed Sacrament|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.cathedralsacramento.org/history-working-page}}</ref>\n|-\n|Divine Mercy\n|\n|2231 Club Center Dr, Sacramento\n|2005\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Divine Mercy Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/divine-mercy-parish-sacramento}}</ref>\n|-\n|Holy Spirit\n|\n|3159 Land Park Dr, Sacramento\n|1940\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Holy Spirit Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/holy-spirit-parish-sacramento}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Our Story|publisher=Holy Spirit Parish|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=http://www.hs-sacramento.org/?page_id=24}}</ref>\n|-\n|Our Lady of Guadalupe National Shrine\n|[[File:Our Lady of Guadalupe Shrine in Sacramento California.jpg|100px]]\n|711 T St, Sacramento\n|1958\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Our Lady of Guadalupe Parish (Santuario Nacional de Nuestra S