anice in [[Nevada City, California|Nevada City]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Canice Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-canice-parish-nevada-city}}</ref> Immaculate Conception in [[Downieville, California|Downieville]];<ref>{{cite web|title=Immaculate Conception Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/immaculate-conception-parish-downieville}}</ref> St. Patrick in [[Weaverville, California|Weaverville]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Patrick Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-patrick-parish-weaverville}}</ref> St. Dominic in [[Benicia, California|Benicia]];<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Dominic Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-dominic-parish-benicia}}</ref> and St. Joseph in [[Marysville, California|Marysville]].<ref>{{cite web|title=St. Joseph Parish|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/st-joseph-parish-marysville}}</ref> \n\n==City Deanery==\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:75%\"\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"30%\" |'''Name'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10%\" |'''Image'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"30%\" |'''Location'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"15\" |'''Established'''\n! style=\"background:darkviolet; color:yellow;\" width=\"10\" |'''Sources'''\n|-\n|[[Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament (Sacramento, California)|Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament]]\n|[[File:CathBSlow.jpg|100px]]\n|1017 11th St, [[Sacramento, California|Sacramento]]\n|1889\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Cathedral of the Blessed Sacrament|publisher=Diocese of Sacramento|accessdate=April 20, 2020|url=https://www.scd.org/parish/cathedral-blessed-sacrament-sacramento}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|t